much easier to use than other autoclickers, love it!","created":"2024-08-01T13:33:56Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":18492070,"name":"Cgg0456","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/18492070/","username":"anonymous-abddac429856c6c87d35bc08c937ca80"},"score":5,"reply":null,"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":2034422,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"Excellent. I suggest to add more clicks...","created":"2024-01-08T15:46:32Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":12592329,"name":"يحيى","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/12592329/","username":"Yahya17"},"score":5,"reply":null,"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1991138,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"This would be great except it only works once. You can only set a delay of X number of seconds for the item to be clicked. After that, it will never be clicked automatically again. It *says* \"click every X seconds,\" but it doesn't click \"every\" anything. Just once.\n\nI want to love it, but I want it to click the button over and over and over and there's no way to set that. I can't figure out why someone would want a button to be clicked only once, but not be willing to do that manually.","created":"2023-08-21T20:56:56Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":18025363,"name":"smeej","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/18025363/","username":"anonymous-dc5fd430a83d1024673cb368a28cefc8"},"score":1,"reply":null,"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1985551,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"It works great on some things but I originally got it to click the next button on this stupid online driving course I'm required to take. Its 8 hours long and its built so you have to keep clicking the next button. But this wont work so I'm looking for other extensions","created":"2023-08-03T22:04:08Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":18002602,"name":"ACelata","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/18002602/","username":"anonymous-d77869bcdc3bca466fcb95a0586a5c9d"},"score":3,"reply":null,"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1974156,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"It would be great if a frequency value is kept on a new tab after it is updated.","created":"2023-06-23T19:23:29Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":17812441,"name":"Jason M","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/17812441/","username":"anonymous-806ed3d83db5592613d6bd7a6c59c6d9"},"score":4,"reply":null,"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1973291,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"Super easy «fácil». In just 10 seconds I had it configured.","created":"2023-06-20T12:31:56Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":5473918,"name":"tipar","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/5473918/","username":"tipar"},"score":5,"reply":null,"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1933512,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"Why can I only select one thing to click?","created":"2023-02-17T23:57:04Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":17761957,"name":"Pluto","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/17761957/","username":"anonymous-e5be0591574f30205f4dcbe4c0303271"},"score":1,"reply":{"id":1934149,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"When I created this small project, I made it to accomplish only one thing- repetitively click an element on a webpage.\nThe extension is open source, so if a community member was interested in enhancing the capabilities, it could be done here: https://github.com/david-shortman/clickster.\nI don't have current plans to enhance this extension, but I hope you're able to find something that fits your use case.","created":"2023-02-19T23:19:28Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":true,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":16458240,"name":"David","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/16458240/","username":"anonymous-951c0c60d5c4674d6a7f491f3da4464f"}},"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1930667,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"Does not seem to work for me in 2023.  Unable to select a target, always says no target selected.","created":"2023-02-09T05:09:20Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":17771451,"name":"mikedufty","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/17771451/","username":"anonymous-f051bb06ed9f3d27c61d2923c6947805"},"score":1,"reply":{"id":1934148,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"Using Firefox v111.0, I'm able to set a target. To select some targets, try pressing the \"Enter\" key while hovering over it. That method should always work, whereas clicking a target may not always work.","created":"2023-02-19T23:15:22Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":true,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":16458240,"name":"David","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/16458240/","username":"anonymous-951c0c60d5c4674d6a7f491f3da4464f"}},"version":{"id":5145375,"version":"1.1.0"}},{"id":1929160,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"I've been trying to find a good add-on that can click a button on it's own when I'm not focused on the tab and almost all of them were unnecessarily specific like made for one button or unnecessarily complicated and required you to code them in javascript. This is perfect.","created":"2023-02-04T01:04:25Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":false,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":17695848,"name":"Firefox user 17695848","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/17695848/","username":"anonymous-e0d11d34149732606ce8defbca58a210"},"score":5,"reply":{"id":1934150,"addon":{"id":2676034,"slug":"clickster","name":{"en-US":"Clickster"},"icon_url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/2676/2676034-64.png?modified=b44b885e"},"body":"Glad to hear it was helpful!","created":"2023-02-19T23:19:59Z","is_deleted":false,"is_developer_reply":true,"is_latest":true,"previous_count":0,"user":{"id":16458240,"name":"David","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/16458240/","username":"anonymous-951c0c60d5c4674d6a7f491f3da4464f"}},"version":{"id":5145